## Call for Proposal

call-for-proposal--title = Call for Proposal
call-for-proposal--body-paragraph-1 =
  If you want to share a creative project or an unusual hack in computing,
  come present your <strong data-l10n-name='talk'>talk</strong>.
call-for-proposal--body-paragraph-2 =
  If you'd rather lead a hands-on, you can run a <strong data-l10n-name='workshop'>workshop</strong>.
call-for-proposal--body-paragraph-3 =
